snippet.textDisplay:
Jitna accha national anthem banate ho utna accha desh bhi banalo to baat hi kya 😢😢😢😢
I am Indian but meri Pakistan se koi aapsi dushmani nhi hai balki humare desh mein pratha chalti hai Vasudeva kutumba kam. Problem is that ki aap tarakki pe nhi neecha dikhane par vishwaas krte hon. Another problem is that ki aapke pas acche leaders nhi hai like our Modi ji.❤❤❤❤
Aap tab proud kre jab aap log actual mein tarakki kre. No doubt ki aap log music mein kaafi acche hon but agr aap Pakistan ki janta jage to aap log Pakistan ko kha se kha leke jaa skte hon yeh aap logo ko bhi nhi pta.
Don't offend, I am just giving my point.
😊😊😊😊😊❤❤
